DESCRIPTION:The 2026 Education & Workforce Summit: King County Career Showc
	ase brings together educators\, employers\, industry leaders\, and communi
	ty partners for a dynamic\, future-focused event centered on building a st
	rong regional talent pipeline. This annual summit highlights emerging work
	force trends\, innovative education strategies\, and the evolving needs of
	 King County's key industries. Participants will have the opportunity to e
	xplore interactive exhibits\, hear from expert panelists\, engage in solut
	ion-driven discussions\, and connect directly with organizations committed
	 to developing the next generation of talent. From K-12 and higher educati
	on to workforce development programs and employers\, the Summit creates a 
	space where collaboration drives meaningful impact. Join us as we showcase
	 new career pathways\, celebrate partnerships\, and work together to equip
	 King County residents with the skills and opportunities needed to thrive 
	in a rapidly changing workforce landscape.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com
	/events/#/details/2026-education-workforce-summit-king-county-career-showc
	ase/17665199/2026-04-23T00
