UID:zB0xWPs3HQCnfzFX-owlF
SUMMARY:Veteran Benefits 101 Workshop Series
DTSTAMP:20260413T005337Z
DTSTART:20260424T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Our Native Veterans & Elders Programs are teaming up with the W
	A’s VA to bring you a Veteran Benefits 101 Workshop series! Whether you ar
	e looking to learn about your eligibility or ready to start an application
	 onsite with an accredited Veteran Service Officer\, we are here to suppor
	t you!  Share this workshop series with the veterans in your community!\n\
	nEvent Details \n\n When: The last Friday of each month\n\n Time: 11 am to
	 1 pm\n\n Where: Labateyah Youth Home\, 9010 13th Ave NW\, Seattle\, WA 98
	117\n\nUpcoming Workshop Topics \n\n March 27: Veterans Benefits Administr
	ation 101 \\(Disability Compensation\, Education\, Home Loans\, Burials\, 
	& more\\)\n\n April 24: Veterans Health Administration 101 \\(VA Hospital 
	& Medical Care\\)\n\n May 29: Veteran Service Officer Networking & Additio
	nal Benefits 101\n\nWhat to Expect \n\n Lunch provided for attendees\n\n G
	ift cards available for veterans\, veteran spouses\, or caretakers of vete
	rans \\(Limit 1 per household\\)\n\n Transportation is available\, if need
	ed\n\n Registration is encouraged to help us prepare: https://forms.office
	.com/r/KrRTQ86ZPr \n\n  \n\nQuestions? Please email us at veterans@unitedi
	ndians.org \n\nNote: Workshop topics and schedules are subject to change. 
	\n\n\\#SeattleVeterans \\#SeattleEvents \\#WashingtonVA \\#SeattleSeniors 
	\\#VeteranBenefits \\#VABenefits \\#ServiceOfficers \\#VeteranSupport \\#M
	ilitaryFamily \\#Veterans101 \\#VeteranResources\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amci
	ty.com/events/#/details/veteran-benefits-101-workshop-series/18443410/2026
	-04-24T00
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/veteran-benefits-101-work
	shop-series/18443410/2026-04-24T00
LOCATION:Labateyah Youth Home\, 9010 13th Ave NW\, Seattle\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
